    "After collecting data, the participants were paid $40 for participating.",
    "All participants consented to data disclosure, and data for all subjects were included in our dataset.",
    "The sensor collection framework used in our study is an adaptation of the ActionSense framework 76.",
    "The original framework encompassing codes, a graphical user interface (GUI), and sensor visualization capabilities was tailored for human-activity data collection from wearable devices during kitchen activities.",
